{
  "stem": "11964.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we were walking through, and we were realizing we were going in the direction of the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was passing a house, which was familiar to me because friends of ours lived there-- had lived there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I said to my friend to my left, I said, for better or for worse, worse, I think that I'm going to have to escape.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, somebody fainted in the back, and there were shouts.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the-- every 10 rows, an SS man was accompanying us with a machine gun at the ready and with a police dog.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the SS men that were policing the front of the column ran back to the back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I squeezed my friend's hand, and I ran.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I ran right into the building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And it was a three or four-story building, and I ran up to the top.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I noticed a bin with coal there, and I just crawled into that bin, closed the lid.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I said, whatever happens happens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I could not keep on worrying any longer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 20, 21 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, all we heard is that they are taking people away to places from where nobody returns.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and the, the conjecture was that these were labor camps, that people are working very hard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did not know of death camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I didn't know of death camps, not at that time, not in January of 1943.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The event I am now describing happened January 6, 1943.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The reason I remember the date because it was a Catholic, Catholic holiday of All Saints, Wszystkich Swietych.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the, the, the, the town was deserted.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
